	<Title>
		Fruit juice: Good or bad for kids?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Fruit juice can be a healthy part of a child&apos;s diet &amp;mdash; if you select carefully.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is it OK to give my child fruit juice?
	</Question>
